	Get rid of all use of nemo_link_get_display_name since
	links all have plain names now.
	
	* libnemo-extensions/nemo-directory-async.c:
	(set_up_request_by_file_attributes): Fix bug that was causing the
	program to get the activation URI for every single icon.  Lots of
	extra I/O! Also changed it to get the file info first since the
	activation URI is now based on MIME type.
	(lacks_activation_uri): Don't try to get the activation URI until
	after the file info is there.
	(activation_uri_done),
	(activation_uri_read_done),
	(activation_uri_nemo_link_read_callback),
	(activation_uri_gmc_link_read_callback),
	(start_getting_activation_uris):
	Changed the code to read the activation URI to use MIME type,
	so now it doesn't have to open every file just to find out if it's
	a GMC link.
	
	* libnemo-extensions/nemo-file-utilities.c:
	(nemo_get_desktop_directory): Get rid of a tiny bit of dead code.
	
	* libnemo-extensions/nemo-file.h:
	* libnemo-extensions/nemo-file.c:
	(nemo_file_contains_text): No need to special-case the link
	file any more because its MIME type will now make it clear it's
	not a text file.  Also removed nemo_file_activate_custom since
	it's not needed any more and moved the logic into
	fm-directory-view.c.
	
	* libnemo-extensions/nemo-icon-factory.c:
	(nemo_icon_factory_get_icon_for_file): Added FIXMEs.
	
	* libnemo-extensions/nemo-link-set.c:
	(nemo_link_set_install): Changed comments to not call link files
	".link" files.
	
	* libnemo-extensions/nemo-global-preferences.h:
