	NEMO_PREFERENCES_SHOW_REAL_FILE_NAME preference since we no
	longer have to lie about file names to make ".link" files
	palatable.

	* libnemo-extensions/nemo-link.h:
	* libnemo-extensions/nemo-link.c: (nemo_link_create):
	Added code that notifies the NemoFile framework that a new file
	has been created, so callers don't have to worry about that.
	(nemo_link_is_link_file): Simplified the code -- turned it into
	a one-liner.
	(nemo_link_set_icon): The old code had half NemoFile calls
	and half sync. I/O. Got rid of the NemoFile stuff. Also put the
	code in to notify the NemoFile framework about the change to
	the file.
